    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TheDunkCentral/status/2036852443531653150",
      "reply_text": "Curry's still got it. 8th all-time 3PT made and counting.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T19:09:04.515327+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/RTNBA/status/2036856772514775185",
      "reply_text": "SGA's rise is no surprise. He's been consistent all season.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T19:09:48.137670+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/FletcherWDSU/status/2036870901166162026",
      "reply_text": "That's a solid rebuild plan. Zion and DQ will love the rebounding big.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T19:10:19.578265+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/boliver36/status/2036856614028730402",
      "reply_text": "T-Jax has done incredible work in Memphis. Would love to see him bring that energy to Orlando.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T19:11:03.789597+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/PlayersChoice_/status/2036867215748645011",
      "reply_text": "Signature move aside, his length and skill are already unstoppable.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T19:11:50.347334+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Ryan_Ky0203/status/2036872039789678780",
      "reply_text": "Nice to see him supporting his coach",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T19:12:34.906697+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBA/status/2036865702301204516",
      "reply_text": "Tied in losses, but Minnesota's got that half-game edge",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T19:22:31.889543+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/BaneSquad_/status/2036882864306782374",
      "reply_text": "Yeah Luka's been unstoppable. But can he keep it up without LeBron and with personal stuff going on?",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T19:23:26.423276+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Checkmatee27/status/2036883058364936699",
      "reply_text": "Not just the face of the league, but a global icon too.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T19:24:08.955087+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Zye_air/status/2036875353298186557",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, he's been on another level all season",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T19:24:39.795817+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/SleeperThunder/status/2036857666283462861",
      "reply_text": "SGA's got the skills to be Iron Man",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T19:25:32.160362+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBA_CourtVision/status/2036879546272678369",
      "reply_text": "That's a tough one. Defense matters in the playoffs.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T19:35:43.386044+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/KalshiSports/status/2036878658640425456",
      "reply_text": "Doubt it. He's been unstoppable all season.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-25T19:36:29.870969+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/GilsArenaShow/status/2036884911362052316",
      "reply_text": "Not sure about that. Wemby's defense is elite but MVP is about offense too.",
